Math problem:
 What is the degree measure of angle $LOQ$ when polygon $\allowbreak LMNOPQ$ is a regular hexagon? [asy]
draw((-2,0)--(-1,1.73205081)--(1,1.73205081)--(2,0)--(1,-1.73205081)--(-1,-1.73205081)--cycle);
